name: NAPD 2 (radiocarbon years)
notes: Chron based on top and estimated age of the top of Artemisia zone. The bulk 14C dates are probably too old, and other evidence indicates a date of .ca 10,000 14C yr BP for top of Artemisia zone (P.T. Davis, pers. comm.).
